Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:25.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macross Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:32.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先于Frontier数年启航的21号巨型移民船团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由大企业设计制定方案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:38.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无保留地投入各种先进技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:42.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航海过程中也继续发展技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:46.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电脑工程学和植入技术上成果卓越
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:50.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一跃成为少数拥有高科技能力的船团之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使是Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Vajra的攻击下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:58.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求援 求援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些臭虫们爬上了主岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:02.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:13.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船体各部件无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:15.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,De-fold成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:20.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认本舰前方02方位达尔特弗和卡利托斯的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:21.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:25.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:29.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 我们的首要任务虽然是救援幸存舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:32.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其同等 甚至更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:36.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集Vajra的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不代表新统合军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是总统阁下的要求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以这样理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:49.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:53.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会留意的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:56.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 投入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:45.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M5和6 M5…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多没来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到我的告别演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间虽然短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:54.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很庆幸能认识Frontier的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生许多事 让大家操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚像平常那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飙出Macross的速度来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我的歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅队长向各机通话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是给军队打头阵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便还要收集Vajra的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试作型空间跳跃通信诱导系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:57.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态良好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有它应该不会再被Vajra扰乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:01.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尽可能靠后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:13.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先跟上我再说 不许走远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:16.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:18.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机 Planet Dance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 路哈尼 彼特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:22.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别又因为看不见我就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真多嘴 葛兰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的事纠缠不休
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:54.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:03.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么笨重的重装型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能被它甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:46.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡纳莉亚 干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:07.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dabind01向达尔特弗通话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:12.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借甲板一用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是达尔特弗 请脚下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.16,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs44}Konig Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(635,655)}怪兽之王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主甲板固定 抗冲击防护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dabind01开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的人都撤出我的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konig Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:36.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物退散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:52.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:57.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆 先保护损伤严重的卡利托斯撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认与Frontier空间跳跃数据链接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:11.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间跳跃通信 数据链接状态良好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延迟为+40
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:16.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一攻击部队 开始与Vajra交战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.45,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs44}Hyperion&Prometheus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(512,655)}土卫七
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(730,655)}土卫十六
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二攻击队正在部署中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯 受损率45%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负伤者众多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先派遣救援部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕的切换不好 查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占优势
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似比想象的优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:46.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:52.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 又到线路上偷听了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 几乎是现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多 怎么还不来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么精彩的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:17.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:25.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实应该亲口告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些难以启齿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作原因 今天回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定会遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那阿鲁多也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:50.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢的那位飞行员似乎也很卖力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:52.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心的是Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且飞行员的工作如果是战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作就是唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯 正撤离战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离空间跳跃安全范围还有450
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种空间断层的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能更早逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开 彼特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:47.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯被炸沉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸存者…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:57.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,径直穿越了空间断层
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Vajra的战舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太靠前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:20.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是必须对它…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束发射器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这种空间跳跃能量反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是空间跳跃牵引器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:43.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-1 发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:45.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡被敌人吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被击落了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:48.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船俘虏并吞掉了卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到最后一首了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必须和大家告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然时间过得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:24.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却留下了美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:27.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在广阔的银河中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能不能重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:35.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:38.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:40.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:44.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:53.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:27.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听我说几句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:31.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一首歌想为某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:35.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是为某些人而唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:39.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为在远方奋战的将士们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:42.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐明知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:54.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道…却
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:14:00.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你…也能一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家 我爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:22.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从绝望中启程的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:31.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有耳边的风声为我们送行…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:37.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 你一个人能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手可是艘刺猬一样的船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他刺猬不刺猬的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:51.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要钻进肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太莽撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡纳莉亚 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜算如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是只乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:58.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 根据SK-3收集的数据模拟运算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最大战斗速度时我们略胜一筹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:02.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部门无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:07.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改装后首次使用 应该能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:09.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:12.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据对方炮击模式编成了回避程序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导航请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贸然出击太过危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算飞行员被困敌人舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:21.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们逃跑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达尔特弗的乘员会被全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy也会安危难料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:34.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛拉斯中尉 你传达的总统要求是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:39.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有实现它的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:48.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自相残杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:00.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:09.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quarter向起飞的所有部队通话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:12.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰即将开始对Vajra母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采取近距离格斗战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:15.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斗战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:17.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于闪亮登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位全力保护达尔特弗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的猎物归我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:26.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 Transformation
